The four point scale you are using to gauge people's behaviors in the game will not be reflective of their actual behavior - I suggest you use a 7-point Likert scale. Also your section on attitudes towards the game can be cleaned up. Not only are the questions far too similar, they are poorly phrased that throw off native English speakers. 

Also, you don't have to provide a gift card for me. 

Thanks.
